# Keep the build context small + reproducible: the compiled artifacts and VCS metadata never belong in it.
# `**/target` (not just the root) — a nested worktree under .claude/worktrees/ carries its own
# target/ tree, and a single unanchored entry keeps every one of them out of the context.
target/
**/target
.git/
# Agent worktrees/session state — never build inputs.
.claude/
# Node/bun installs + web build output — the web image runs `bun install` + `bun run build` fresh, so a
# host tree must never clobber the freshly-installed deps or leak a stale build into the image.
node_modules
**/node_modules
web/build
web/.react-router
